#ingame
#######

^#5aa9d6;Allows hammers and axes to glow when ready while still benefitting from racial buffs.^reset;

This mod is required in order to restore full functionality of both mods. Requires Frackin' Races and Windup Weapons Glow to work.

Check out Argle Bargles Easier Hammers and Axes or my own Windup Weapons Glow for other windup options.

For more, click the MEGATHREAD link from the steam page.

